<!-- ##### SECTION Title ##### -->
SexyTooltip

<!-- ##### SECTION Short_Description ##### -->
A tooltip-like window container which allows arbitrary widgets as children.

<!-- ##### SECTION Long_Description ##### -->
<para>
SexyTooltip is a GtkWindow which mimics the appearance of a normal gtk+
tooltip, but allows arbitrary widgets rather than just text.
</para>

